text: Éva Izsák (born 8 August 1967) is a road cyclist from Hungary. She represented her nation at the 1992 Summer Olympics in the women's road race. ==References== ==External links== * profile at sports-reference.com Category:Hungarian female cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Hungary Category:Living people Category:People from Mosonmagyaróvár Category:1967 births
